Params: {2: '???', 3: 'Did you really think that you can withstand both the corruption from the virus and Tenebrion, with just your will alone?', 4: '2'}
{2: '???', 3: 'Then have you ever considered that, without my help, where you would have been now?', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: "No matter what, I'm not giving up hope. I'll never become corrupted.", 4: '1'}
{2: '???', 3: 'Hah, such empty words you speak. At least you have that going for you.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: 'Nice of you to compliment me for once.', 4: '1'}
{2: '???', 3: 'I will enjoy the moment when you fall.', 4: '2'}
